chat.msg: Welcome!
Hello,
Hello! I'm the navigator. What can I help you with today?
You will begin our travels by the map.
Great! Could you please describe the starting point on the map?
Proceed across the land and water at an angel that takes you to the corner of the island with the tiger on it. You want to go near the tip of that island.

Understood. I will proceed across the land and water at an angle towards the corner of the island with the tiger. Once I reach the island, I will head towards the tip. 

I have arrived at the island with the tiger. What's the next instruction?
Travel around that large boulder like mass keeping it on your right and the tip of the island on your left.

Got it! I will navigate around the large boulder-like mass, keeping it on my right and the tip of the island on my left. 

I have successfully circled around the boulder-like mass. What's the next instruction?
You will now exit the land and travel acrid water agin toward the island withe the parrot.

Alright! I will exit the land and travel across the water towards the island with the parrot. 

I have arrived at the island with the parrot. What's the next instruction?
You will travel toward the upper tip of that island at an angel that goes above the head of the parrot.

Got it! I will travel towards the upper tip of the island with the parrot, following an angle that goes above the head of the parrot.

I have reached the upper tip of the island. What should I do next?
Take a downward turn between the bodies of the elephant and the parrot and then circle back to head toward the island with the frog.

Understood! I will take a downward turn between the bodies of the elephant and the parrot, and then circle back to head towards the island with the frog.

I have reached the island with the frog. What's the next instruction?
Keeping the frog on your lefthand side pass the body of the frog fully and then circle back to have the body of the frog on your right and the mass of trees on your left.

Got it! I will keep the frog on my left-hand side and pass its body fully. Then, I will circle back to have the body of the frog on my right and the mass of trees on my left.

I have completed the circle and now the body of the frog is on my right and the mass of trees is on my left. What would you like me to do next?
You will then proceed to cross back via the alligator to the island that has the elephant and the frog...but this time you will be at the bottom tip crossing the large boulder.

Understood! I will proceed to cross back via the alligator to the island that has the elephant and the frog. This time, I will be at the bottom tip and cross the large boulder.

I have reached the island with the elephant and the frog, crossing the large boulder at the bottom tip. What's the next instruction?

chat.msg: Welcome!
How do I start
To start, you are currently at the top-right corner of the map where a white dog is sitting. Can you see the dog?
yes
Great! Now, let's begin by taking a few steps to your left (west), below a wooden bench. Can you see the wooden bench?
yes
Wonderful! Now, after going below the wooden bench, there is a trail in front of you. Cross the trail and continue heading towards a florist stand. Can you see the florist stand?
yes
Fantastic! But instead of reaching the florist stand, make a left turn and cross the trail again. Head back towards the white dog. Can you see the white dog again?
The navigation is easy to understand but difficult to make move
I understand that it may be challenging to physically move, but let's continue the navigation in our dialogue. Can you please confirm if you can see the white dog again?
yes
Great! Now, just near the white dog, you will see a wooden branch crossing a river. Cross over the branch and continue heading south. Can you see the wooden branch and the river?
yes
Excellent! Keep heading southwards after crossing the branch. There will be another white dog sitting next to a red and white checkered picnic. Can you see the picnic and the white dog?
yes
Perfect! Now, walk over the picnic mat, touch the bowl of berries, and continue heading west. Can you see the mat and the bowl of berries?
yes
Great job! Next, you will come across another wooden branch that crosses the river. Cross over the branch, this time heading north. Can you see the wooden branch and the river?
yes

Well done! After crossing the river, you will notice a green bush. Instead of touching the bush, circle around it from the right, until you reach the florist stand. Can you see the green bush and the florist stand?
yes

Fantastic! Now, make a left turn (west) below the florist stand and continue until you reach a big bridge. On the bridge, you will see two people riding a bicycle. Can you see the bridge and the people riding the bicycle?
yes
Great observation! Now, pass the bridge to the west. Just after the bridge, you will notice two elderly people sitting on a bench, reading newspapers. Can you spot the bench and the elderly people?
yes

Amazing! Now, take a few steps south, between the old people and another wooden branch. Once you're through, you will reach a green bush next to the end of the wooden branch. Can you see the wooden branch and the green bush?
yes
Wonderful! Now, go east, between the wooden branch and the green bush. Take a few steps in that direction. Can you describe what you see around you?
a deer
Excellent! You've made it to the next landmark. Just a few steps to the east, there is a brown young deer. Congratulations, you have reached the final objective! Well done!

chat.msg: Welcome!
Doyou see the teepee
Yes, I see the tent, which I assume is the same as the teepee. I am currently at the tent. What should I do next?
Start there and head toward the dog keeping the dog on your left as you pass it and head to the flame.
Got it! I will start at the tent and head towards the dog, keeping it on my left. Then, I will continue towards the flame. Should I pass the flame on my left or my right?
On your right and then travel toward the mushroom keeping the mushroom on your left and traveling past it as well.
Understood! I will pass the flame on my right and then continue towards the mushroom, keeping it on my left. I will travel past the mushroom as well. What's next?
Travel on the path toward the blue car and go into the dead end near the car and then exit back out and continue to go down the path

Great! I will travel on the path towards the blue car and then go into the dead end near the car. After that, I will exit back out and continue going down the path. Is there anything specific I should look out for or any turns I need to make?
Yes, look for the blue telescope and travel keeping it on your right.
Thank you for the instruction. I will keep an eye out for the blue telescope and travel while keeping it on my right. Once I reach the telescope, what should I do next?
Go between the telescope and the large shrub and circle on the path toward the log cabin.
Got it! Once I reach the blue telescope, I will go between the telescope and the large shrub, circling on the path towards the log cabin. Should I continue on the path until I reach the cabin?
Right before the end of the path you will cross onto the grass and climb over a few boulders to reach the porch of the cabin.

Alright! So, right before the end of the path, I will cross onto the grass and climb over a few boulders to reach the porch of the cabin. Once I am on the cabin's porch, does that mean I have reached the final destination?

chat.msg: Welcome!
Where do I start
You start at the top, near a group of three palm trees. Can you see the palm trees?
yes
Great! Now, go under the first tree and head towards the south-west. Let me know when you're there.
Toward what
Go towards the south-west. Imagine standing at the top and facing the palm trees. The south-west direction is diagonally to your left and downwards. Let me know when you're there.
Do I head toward the dog or the speaker

You should head towards the south-west without paying attention to the dog or the speaker at the moment. Focus on the direction, not on any specific landmarks. Let me know once you've reached the south-west.
I am there
Great job! Now, turn right and cross the second palm tree. Let me know when you've crossed it.
I have
Perfect! Now, take a sharp left turn before the third palm tree and continue heading south. Let me know when you're heading south.
Okay done
Awesome! As you continue south, you'll come across a brown puppy. Stay slightly to the left of the puppy and then turn right to continue heading south. Let me know when you've made the right turn.
Done

Great work! Now, as you keep going south, you'll reach a point where there's a big rock on your left and a small rock on your right. Walk between them and keep heading towards the water. Let me know when you've reached the water.
Done

Fantastic! Now that you're at the water, face right and you'll see a large red crab. Turn right (west) and follow the coastline, keeping the big rock on your left. Let me know when you've turned right and started moving west.
Done

Excellent! As you continue along the water, you'll come across a medium-sized rock. Keep going until you reach the third medium rock. Once you're there, you'll see a shark in the water. Make a sharp turn to the right. Let me know when you've made the sharp right turn.
Done

Well done! Now, you'll need to head back to the land. Walk between the medium-sized rock and a blue-yellow-white ball and continue heading north. Let me know when you're on land again and heading north.
Done

Great progress! Now, veer slightly left and head towards the north-west. You'll be crossing between a red tent on your left and a larger speaker on your right. Let me know when you've crossed between them.
Done

Awesome job! Now, you're going to circle around the red tent in an arc. After that, continue heading south towards the sea. Just as you reach the shore, make a right turn (west) and go below a red kayak. Let me know when you've made the right turn and are below the red kayak.
Done

Fantastic! Now, here's your next instruction: make a 90-degree right turn (north) and move along the kayak. Keep going until you reach a small green bush. Let me know when you've reached the small green bush.
Done
Congratulations! You have successfully reached your final objective, the small green bush. Well done on following the path accurately and completing the navigation. Great job!
Done

Well done! You successfully completed the navigation and reached the small green bush. Great job following the instructions and finding your way! If you have any other questions or need further assistance, feel free to ask.
None
Alright then! If you ever need help with anything else in the future, don't hesitate to ask. Have a great day!
